FBIS4-6618 "dreas078_a_94013" FBIS-EAS-94-078 Daily Report 22 Apr 1994 NORTHEAST ASIA Japan Kono on `Double Power Structure' Kono on `Double Power Structure' OW2204131094 Tokyo NHK General Television Network in Japanese 1008 GMT 22 Apr 94 OW2204131094 Tokyo NHK General Television Network Japanese BFN [Announcer-read report over video: from "NHK News 7" program] [Text] Liberal Democratic Party President Yohei Kono stresses his determination to have a showdown with the new administration. [Begin recording] I feel this is a Shinseito [Japan Renewal Party] administration. If we asked Hata what he thinks of being a candidate for the premiership, he would answer that he is a player while another person writes the scenarios. Well, I cannot help saying that the coalition still has a double power structure. [end recording]
